                <h2 class="he mb-2"> Aarogya Rath - CanWinn Foundation</h2>
                <p>
                    Aarogya Rath, we are committed to fostering a healthier society through our parent organization, the CanWinn Foundation, established by Dr. D.P. Goyal in March 2019. Our mission is to raise public awareness and educate individuals about their health, contributing to the vision of a "Swasth Bharat (स्वस्थ भारत)".                </p>

