            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <h2 class="he mb-2 text-center"> Welcome to CanWinn <br> Aarogya Rath</h2>
                <div class="text-center">
                    <p>Aarogya Rath by Canwinn Hospital brings healthcare directly to you through mobile health units equipped with modern medical facilities and staffed by professionals. We prioritize proactive healthcare, empowering individuals with knowledge to lead healthier lives while offering services from preventive check-ups to specialized treatments. Located in Sector 45, Gurugram, the Canwinn Seva Polyclinic is our flagship facility, providing comprehensive care with advanced infrastructure and expert staff.</p>
